    - Added HomeDirectory()
    - Added TemporaryDirectory()
    - Added more tests

0.02_02 2009-10-01 17:02
    - Use Module::Install
    - Cleanup POD

0.02_01 2009-10-01 10:22
    - Added support for DomainMask
    - Added support for returning multiple directories

0.01  2009-09-30 23:22
